author: Jessica Morrey
title: Friday Night Lights Scoreboard - Week 8
text: Updated: Thursday, October 15 2015 3:49 PM EDT 2015-10-15 19:49:17 GMT IRVING, Texas – Baylor men’s basketball has been picked to finish fifth in the 2016 Big 12 Conference preseason poll. The Bears received 49 points and trailed Kansas (81), Oklahoma (70), Iowa State (68) and Texas (51).This marks the fifth time in the last six seasons that the Bears have been projected to finish in the top half of the league. BU was picked sixth last year and finished tied for fourth, earning a No. 3 seed in the NCAA Tournament for a second consecutive ...
